'''联邦咨询委员会法'''（Federal Advisory Committee Act）是[[美国|美国]]一部规范联邦咨询委员会行为的[[美国法律|联邦法律]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Federal Advisory Committee Act|url=http://www.gsa.gov/portal/content/100916|accessdate=20 July 2012|author=Committee Management Secretariat|date=15 June 2012|work=Federal Advisory Committee Management - Legislation and Regulations|publisher=U.S. General Services Administration|archive-date=2017-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719212427/https://www.gsa.gov/portal/content/100916|dead-url=no}}</ref>。联邦咨询委员会法将联邦咨询委员会定义为向[[美国总统|美国总统]]提供 "意见或建议"的临时机构<ref>{{Cite book|title=Federal Advisory Committee Act 3(2), 9(b)|year=1972|publisher=U.S. House of Representatives|url=http://www.gsa.gov/graphics/ogp/without_annotations_R2G-b4T_0Z5RDZ-i34K-pR.pdf|accessdate=2012-07-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120916205929/http://www.gsa.gov/graphics/ogp/without_annotations_R2G-b4T_0Z5RDZ-i34K-pR.pdf|archivedate=2012-09-16}}</ref>。

